commitResults.messageBody:
(ParserUtilTest)remove parseAddress_invalidValue_throwsParseException()
because Address can be empty.

(AddCommandParserTest)remove missing email and address prefix tests
because Address and Email can be empty upon creation of contact.

(EmailTest)remove assertFalse empty email
because Email can be empty.

(AddressTest)remove assertFalse empty address
because Address can be empty.

(PersonTest)modify isSamePerson()
because now two contacts are duplicate iff they have the same
(Name, Phone).
